PrecisReappointment of MICHEL OUIMET, of Saint-Siméon de Bonaventure, Quebec, as Chairperson of the Boards of Referees for the Quebec Regional Division, and particularly for the District of Gaspé, for a term of three years, effective April 16, 1999.
